#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.178"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.178:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.178:0.2"
msgid "18. Sañcetaniyavagga "
msgstr "18. Intention "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: cetovimuttisuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.178:0.3"
msgid "178. Jambālīsutta "
msgstr "178. Billabong "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.178:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.178:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.178:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ santaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "Take a mendicant who enters and remains in a peaceful release of the heart. "

msgctxt "an4.178:1.4"
msgid "So sakkāyanirodhaṃ manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They focus on the cessation of identification, "

msgctxt "an4.178:1.5"
msgid "Tassa sakkāyanirodhaṃ manasi karoto sakkāyanirodhe cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati nādhimuccati. "
msgstr "but their mind isn’t eager, confident, settled, and decided about it. "

#. VAR: Tassa kho evaṃ → tassa kho etaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1) | evaṃ kho tassa (?)
msgctxt "an4.178:1.6"
msgid "Tassa kho evaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno na sakkāyanirodho pāṭikaṅkho. "
msgstr "You wouldn’t expect that mendicant to stop identifying. "

#. VAR: lepagatena → lasagatena (bj, pts1) | lapagatena (s1-3)
#. VAR: gaṇheyyapi → gaṇheyyāpi (pts1) | gayheyyapi (?)
#. VAR: bajjheyyapi → khajjeyyapi (bj) | bajjheyyāpi (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.178:1.7"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso lepagatena hatthena sākhaṃ gaṇheyya, tassa so hattho sajjeyyapi gaṇheyyapi bajjheyyapi; "
msgstr "Suppose a person were to grab a branch with a glue-smeared hand. Their hand would stick, hold, and bind to it. "

msgctxt "an4.178:1.8"
msgid "evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ santaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "In the same way, take a mendicant who enters and remains in a peaceful release of the heart. "

msgctxt "an4.178:1.9"
msgid "So sakkāyanirodhaṃ manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They focus on the cessation of identification, "

msgctxt "an4.178:1.10"
msgid "Tassa sakkāyanirodhaṃ manasi karoto sakkāyanirodhe cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati nādhimuccati. "
msgstr "but their mind isn’t eager, confident, settled, and decided about it. "

#. VAR: Tassa kho evaṃ → tassa kho etaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1) | evaṃ kho tassa (?)
msgctxt "an4.178:1.11"
msgid "Tassa kho evaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno na sakkāyanirodho pāṭikaṅkho. "
msgstr "You wouldn’t expect that mendicant to stop identifying. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.166, sc2
msgctxt "an4.178:2.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ santaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "Next, take a mendicant who enters and remains in a peaceful release of the heart. "

msgctxt "an4.178:2.2"
msgid "So sakkāyanirodhaṃ manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They focus on the cessation of identification, "

msgctxt "an4.178:2.3"
msgid "Tassa sakkāyanirodhaṃ manasi karoto sakkāyanirodhe cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati adhimuccati. "
msgstr "and their mind is eager, confident, settled, and decided about it. "

msgctxt "an4.178:2.4"
msgid "Tassa kho evaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno sakkāyanirodho pāṭikaṅkho. "
msgstr "You’d expect that mendicant to stop identifying. "

msgctxt "an4.178:2.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso suddhena hatthena sākhaṃ gaṇheyya, tassa so hattho neva sajjeyya na gaṇheyya na bajjheyya; "
msgstr "Suppose a person were to grab a branch with a clean hand. Their hand wouldn’t stick, hold, or bind to it. "

msgctxt "an4.178:2.6"
msgid "evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ santaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "In the same way, take a mendicant who enters and remains in a peaceful release of the heart. "

msgctxt "an4.178:2.7"
msgid "So sakkāyanirodhaṃ manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They focus on the cessation of identification, "

msgctxt "an4.178:2.8"
msgid "Tassa sakkāyanirodhaṃ manasi karoto sakkāyanirodhe cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati adhimuccati. "
msgstr "and their mind is eager, confident, settled, and decided about it. "

msgctxt "an4.178:2.9"
msgid "Tassa kho evaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno sakkāyanirodho pāṭikaṅkho. "
msgstr "You’d expect that mendicant to stop identifying. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.178:3.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ santaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "Next, take a mendicant who enters and remains in a peaceful release of the heart. "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.2"
msgid "So avijjāppabhedaṃ manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They focus on smashing ignorance, "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.3"
msgid "Tassa avijjāppabhedaṃ manasi karoto avijjāppabhede cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati nādhimuccati. "
msgstr "but their mind isn’t eager, confident, settled, and decided about it. "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.4"
msgid "Tassa kho evaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno na avijjāppabhedo pāṭikaṅkho. "
msgstr "You wouldn’t expect that mendicant to smash ignorance. "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, jambālī anekavassagaṇikā. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a billabong that had been stagnant for many years. "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.6"
msgid "Tassā puriso yāni ceva āyamukhāni tāni pidaheyya, yāni ca apāyamukhāni tāni vivareyya, devo ca na sammā dhāraṃ anuppaveccheyya. "
msgstr "And someone was to close off the inlets and open up the drains, and the heavens didn’t provide enough rain. "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.7"
msgid "Evañhi tassā, bhikkhave, jambāliyā na āḷippabhedo pāṭikaṅkho. "
msgstr "You wouldn’t expect that billabong to break its banks. "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.8"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ santaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "In the same way, take a mendicant who enters and remains in a certain peaceful release of the heart. "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.9"
msgid "So avijjāppabhedaṃ manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They focus on smashing ignorance, "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.10"
msgid "Tassa avijjāppabhedaṃ manasi karoto avijjāppabhede cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati nādhimuccati. "
msgstr "but their mind isn’t eager, confident, settled, and decided about it. "

msgctxt "an4.178:3.11"
msgid "Tassa kho evaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno na avijjāppabhedo pāṭikaṅkho. "
msgstr "You wouldn’t expect that mendicant to smash ignorance. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.167, sc4
msgctxt "an4.178:4.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ santaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "Next, take a mendicant who enters and remains in a peaceful release of the heart. "

msgctxt "an4.178:4.2"
msgid "So avijjāppabhedaṃ manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They focus on smashing ignorance, "

msgctxt "an4.178:4.3"
msgid "Tassa avijjāppabhedaṃ manasi karoto avijjāppabhede cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati adhimuccati. "
msgstr "and their mind is eager, confident, settled, and decided about it. "

